My Friends Hot Mom - Amanda Blow
Added: February 24, 2011

Amanda has invited Xander, her son's friend, over to her place to have a little talk. Seems he's been dressing nice, driving a new car, and flashing cash, so she figures he's selling drugs. Sure, she doesn't want her son doing any drugs, but claims that she actually wants some for herself so that she can really enjoy a party she's set to attend. Denying the charge up and down, Xander explains that he's simply got a good job, is doing well for himself, and is in no way selling drugs! Eventually deciding he's telling the truth, she admits that though she was sure he was into some bad stuff she made up the story about needing drugs to try and trick him. In fact she's really horny, and figured one of two things: 1. If he were selling drugs then she'd banish him from hanging out with her kid. 2. If he wasn't then she'd finally have him alone in the house so that she could fuck him. Luckily for Xander it looks like he's going to get laid.
